'From Squeak3.10.2 of ''5 June 2008'' [latest update: #7179] on 2 April 2010 at 7:58:47 am'!"Change Set:		FT2PluginHeaderFix-ikpDate:			2 April 2010Author:			Ian Piumartafreetype-config -cflags adds /usr/include/freetype2 to include paths under which exists freetype/tttables.h so we need to use the two-level relative path when including that file."!!FT2Plugin class methodsFor: 'translation' stamp: 'ikp 4/2/2010 07:55'!declareCVarsIn: cg	cg addHeaderFile: '<ft2build.h>'.	cg addHeaderFile: '<freetype/tttables.h>'.	cg addHeaderFile: 'FT_FREETYPE_H'.	cg addHeaderFile: 'FT_OUTLINE_H'.	cg var: 'library' declareC: 'FT_Library library'.	cg var: 'errorCode' type: 'int'.! !